---
---

<section id="about" aria-labelledby="about-label">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label" id="about-label">About</p>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-photo" role="img" aria-label="Photo of Agnislav Onufriichuk">Your photo</div>
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2>From code to<br />culture.</h2>
        <p>I'm a hands-on engineering leader who's spent nearly two decades at the intersection of building software and building teams. I've led orgs from 3 to 15+ engineers, <strong>shipped MVPs to production in under a month</strong>, and established delivery processes that let teams operate without bottlenecks or bus factors.</p>
        <p>I'm not the kind of leader who stops writing code. I still refactor core modules, evaluate testing frameworks, and introduce tooling — like bringing <strong>AI-assisted development workflows</strong> to my teams. But my real impact is in <strong>translating business goals into engineering execution</strong>: architecture decisions, hiring, process design, and getting products to market.</p>
        <p>I've done this across industries — crypto wallets, streaming platforms, travel marketplaces, and e-commerce — always in cross-cultural, distributed environments.</p>
        <div class="about-open">
          <p><strong>Currently open to Head of Engineering, VP of Engineering, or CTO roles</strong> at product companies and startups where engineering leadership is a competitive advantage.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
  }

  .about-photo {
    width: 280px;
    height: 340px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--border), #d4d2ca);
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .about-photo {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--border), #3a3a36);
  }

  .about-text h2 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .about-text p {
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .about-text p :global(strong) {
    color: var(--fg);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .about-open {
    margin-top: 28px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: background-color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .about-open p {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }
    .about-photo {
      width: 100%;
      height: 200px;
    }
  }
</style>
